f scrambled eggs. \u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe cheese might drip down out of the tin, so we recommend placing it on a baking sheet to avoid burnt cheese on the bottom of your oven.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eDid this dish get all 5 stars tonight? We want to know! Head to Plated.com or log on to the mobile app to give us your scores.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["8\" medium pot","12\" large high-sided pan","baking sheet"],"id":4711,"ingredients":["baby spinach","basil","yellow onion","garlic","jar marinara sauce","penne pasta","heavy cream","shredded mozzarella cheese","grated Parmesan cheese","ricotta cheese","aluminum tin"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"baby spinach","quantity":"3.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/7/medium_square_spinach-2.jpg"},{"name":"basil","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1274/medium_square_medium_square_basil-test.jpg"},{"name":"yellow onion","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/27/medium_square_yellow-onion-test.jpg"},{"name":"garlic","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"clove","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2/medium_square_GARLIC_PEELED_copy.jpg"},{"name":"jar marinara sauce","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/77/medium_square_tomato-saauce.jpg"},{"name":"penne pasta","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/428/medium_square_BARILLA_PENNE_PASTA_copy.jpg"},{"name":"heavy cream","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"container","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2301/medium_square_HEAVY_CREAM_copy.jpg"},{"name":"shredded mozzarella cheese","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2325/medium_square_shredded-cheese-moz.jpg"},{"name":"grated Parmesan cheese","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2308/medium_square_PARM_copy.jpg"},{"name":"ricotta cheese","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1486/medium_square_RICOTTA_CHEESE_-4386_copy.jpg"},{"name":"aluminum tin","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/830/medium_square_square_baking_tin.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":14,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/46283/recipe_card_size_jbuGtk0xS6SKd7J54Yjh_2018-04-12__DS_18214504.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. Bring a medium pot of water to a boil over high heat. Rinse \u003cstrong\u003espinach\u003c/strong\u003e and pat dry with paper towel. Rinse \u003cstrong\u003ebasil\u003c/strong\u003e and roughly chop leaves, discarding stems. Peel \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e, halve, and thinly slice. Mince \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Make sauce","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/46284/recipe_card_size_XV5mgImfQrmvQTsZDsq2_2018-04-12__DS_18214511.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eHeat \u003cstrong\u003e.5 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e in a large high-sided pan over medium-high heat. When oil is shimmering, add \u003cstrong\u003eonion\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003egarlic\u003c/strong\u003e and cook, stirring, until softened, 3-4 minutes. Add \u003cstrong\u003emarinara sauce\u003c/strong\u003e, bring to a simmer, and cook until slightly thickened, 3-4 minutes.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook penne","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/46285/recipe_card_size_oqEVkPezQseW1ef4njdl_2018-04-12__DS_18214515.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile sauce simmers, season boiling water generously with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e. Stir in \u003cstrong\u003epenne\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until almost al dente, about 7 minutes (it will continue cooking in the oven). Then, drain and set aside.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Finish sauce","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/46286/recipe_card_size_xMjTMR3AQcSsvZQaCNYM_2018-04-12__DS_18214514.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile pasta cooks, stir \u003cstrong\u003e.25 cup heavy cream\u003c/strong\u003e into sauce, still over medium-high heat, and cook until warmed through, about 1 minute more (see recipe tip). Season with \u003cstrong\u003e.5 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e. Remove pan from heat.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Bake penne","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/46287/recipe_card_size_vzPgGbjKRp6xujufyAi3_5._Assemble_and_Bake_Penne_2X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eOnce cooked, stir \u003cstrong\u003epenne\u003c/strong\u003e into pan with sauce, still off heat, along with \u003cstrong\u003espinach\u003c/strong\u003e. Reshape \u003cstrong\u003etin\u003c/strong\u003e if bent, then pour in \u003cstrong\u003epenne\u003c/strong\u003e and spread in an even layer. Sprinkle over \u003cstrong\u003emozzarella\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e. Dollop over \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of ricotta\u003c/strong\u003e (save remainder for a snack). Place \u003cstrong\u003etin\u003c/strong\u003e on a baking sheet (see recipe tip) and bake until pasta is golden and bubbling, about 12 minutes.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate creamy baked penne","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/46288/recipe_card_size_IZgraTjRdmxoaNdIz1gg_2018-04-12__DS_18214528.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile penne bakes, use this downtime to catch up on dishes or pour a glass of something special. Divide \u003cstrong\u003ecreamy baked penne\u003c/strong\u003e between serving bowls, garnish with \u003cstrong\u003ebasil\u003c/strong\u003e and \u003cstrong\u003eremaining Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e, and dig in!\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""}],"allergens":[{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Pasta","slug":"pasta","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""}],"feature":[]}}